            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_208gc' title='Col. 208GC &mdash; HL Deb 29 January 2004 vol 656 c208GC' name='column_208gc' href='#column_208gc' rel='bookmark'>208GC</a>
            for the report wholly or in part to be based on the random sample. My concern is with the word, "wholly".
          </p>
