      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_213gc' title='Col. 213GC &mdash; HL Deb 29 January 2004 vol 656 c213GC' name='column_213gc' href='#column_213gc' rel='bookmark'>213GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-02473'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040129_GCR_95' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 5 [<span class="italic">Revision of procedures in light of report</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-02474'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040129_GCR_96' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendment No. 51 had been withdrawn from the Marshalled List</span>.]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-02475'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040129_GCR_97' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 5 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-02476'>
