      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-02546'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040129_GCR_168' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Bill reported without amendment.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-02547'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040129_GCR_169' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The Committee adjourned at five minutes before six o'clock.
      </p>
